Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENT

Title: Relates to the source of tax revenues paid to the Deer Park Volunteer Exempt Firemen's Benevolent Association for fire department use and benefit
Summary: Relates to the source of tax revenues paid to the Deer Park Volunteer Exempt Firemen's Benevolent Association for fire department use and benefit.
LawSection: Volunteer and Exempt Firefighters' Benevolent Assoc., Inc.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 535 of the laws of 1968 relating to the incorporation of the Deer Park Volunteer Exempt Firemen's Benevolent Association, and providing for its powers and duties, in relation to the source of tax revenues paid to such association for fire department use and benefit
